title: Blazing 5 - Week 16
itunes:title: Blazing 5 - Week 16
description:
Colin goes over his Blazing 5 picks with RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio who tells him which games the wise guys in Vegas agree or disagree with. Here are the games Colin and RJ go over in week 16:


Ravens @ Browns

Bengals @ Dolphins

Steelers @ Jets

Cowboys @ Eagles

Chiefs @ Bears


Plus, Colin reveals a 6th bonus pick exclusive to this podcast and they even talk some Ohio State vs Clemson
